  <entry>
    <title>安卓免root部署青龙面板</title>
    <link href="/2023/09/15/%E9%9D%92%E9%BE%99/"/>
    <url>/2023/09/15/%E9%9D%92%E9%BE%99/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><h2 id="什么是青龙面板"><a href="#什么是青龙面板" class="headerlink" title="什么是青龙面板"></a>什么是青龙面板</h2><p>青龙面板是支持 Python3、JavaScript、Shell、Typescript 的定时任务管理平台并且支持手机，电脑，棒子（随身wifi）机顶盒 玩客云 服务器等linux平台。羊毛党的必备之品(¯▽¯)👍</p><h2 id="为什么要在手机上装"><a href="#为什么要在手机上装" class="headerlink" title="为什么要在手机上装"></a>为什么要在手机上装</h2><p>在手机上装的优势就是可以随时随地管理面板主要是便携和省点省钱，手机无论你在哪都是必备物品。如果你只是自己跑一些脚本玩不做京东ck头子可以用手机来玩完全够用。不必担心cpu和运存占用情况，这个装在手机上可比国内某绿色二字聊天软件低的多多比上面说的某软件比起来差不多占用是它的十五分之一。</p><h2 id="青龙面板的功能"><a href="#青龙面板的功能" class="headerlink" title="青龙面板的功能"></a>青龙面板的功能</h2><ul><li>支持多种脚本语言（python3、javaScript、shell、typescript）</li><li>支持在线管理脚本、环境变量、配置文件</li><li>支持在线查看任务日志</li><li>支持秒级任务设置</li><li>支持暗黑模式</li><li>支持手机端操作</li></ul><h1 id="如何安装"><a href="#如何安装" class="headerlink" title="如何安装"></a>如何安装</h1><h2 id="所需要的东西"><a href="#所需要的东西" class="headerlink" title="所需要的东西"></a>所需要的东西</h2><ol><li>Zerotermux</li></ol><a class="btn" href="https://www.123pan.com/s/WV06Vv-2rCEd.html"  target="_blank">点我下载</a><ol start="2"><li>一双灵巧的双手和智慧的大脑</li></ol><h2 id="开始安装"><a href="#开始安装" class="headerlink" title="开始安装"></a>开始安装</h2><ol><li>下载并打开Zerotermux，输入如下命令并回车或取存储权限会有一个弹窗点允许就行</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">termux-setup-storage <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="group-image-container"><div class="group-image-row"><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/09/15/S30915-05481295_com.termux.jpg"></div></div></div><p>2.从屏幕左侧向右滑动呼出菜单点击切换源再点击清华源，接下来会自动换源如遇到停顿就点回车此过程需要点多次回车</p><div class="group-image-container"><div class="group-image-row"><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/09/15/S30915-06051672_com.termux.jpg"></div></div></div><ol start="3"><li>输入如下命令并回车执行拉取安装alpine的脚本</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">curl -LO https://raw.githubusercontents.com/Hax4us/TermuxAlpine/master/TermuxAlpine.sh <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="group-image-container"><div class="group-image-row"><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/09/15/S30915-06325472_com.termux.jpg"></div><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/09/15/S30915-06332294_com.termux.jpg"></div></div></div><ol start="4"><li>再输入下面的命令执行刚才拉取的脚本</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">bash TermuxAlpine.sh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure> <div class="group-image-container"><div class="group-image-row"><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/09/15/S30915-07073839_com.termux.jpg"></div><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/09/15/S30915-07080019_com.termux.jpg"></div></div></div><ol start="5"><li>执行命令进入alpine容器里</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">startalpine <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure> <div class="group-image-container"><div class="group-image-row"><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/09/15/S30915-07212856_com.termux.jpg"></div><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/09/15/S30915-07214665_com.termux.jpg"></div></div></div><ol start="6"><li>运行下列一键安装青龙面板的命令，接下来会自动安装青龙面板等待脚本运行结束</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">set</span> -x \<br>&amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n\</span><br><span class="hljs-string">export QL_DIR=/ql\n\</span><br><span class="hljs-string">export QL_BRANCH=develop\n\</span><br><span class="hljs-string">export LANG=zh_CN.UTF-8\n\</span><br><span class="hljs-string">export TERMUX_APK_RELEASE=F-DROID\n\</span><br><span class="hljs-string">export SHELL=/bin/bash\n\</span><br><span class="hljs-string">export PNPM_HOME=~/.local/share/pnpm\n\</span><br><span class="hljs-string">export PATH=<span class="hljs-variable">$PATH</span>:~/.local/share/pnpm:~/.local/share/pnpm/global/5/node_modules\n&quot;</span> \<br>&gt;&gt; /etc/profile.d/ql_env.sh \<br>&amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">source</span> /etc/profile \<br>&amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> -e <span class="hljs-string">&quot;nameserver 119.29.29.29\n\</span><br><span class="hljs-string">nameserver 8.8.8.8&quot;</span> &gt; /etc/resolv.conf \<br>&amp;&amp; sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;s/dl-cdn.alpinelinux.org/mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/g&#x27;</span> /etc/apk/repositories \<br>&amp;&amp; apk update -f \<br>&amp;&amp; apk upgrade \<br>&amp;&amp; apk --no-cache add -f bash make nodejs npm \<br>coreutils moreutils git curl wget tzdata perl \<br>openssl nginx jq openssh python3 py3-pip \<br>&amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span> -rf /var/cache/apk/* \<br>&amp;&amp; apk update \<br>&amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">ln</span> -sf /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai /etc/localtime \<br>&amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Asia/Shanghai&quot;</span> &gt; /etc/timezone \<br>&amp;&amp; npm config <span class="hljs-built_in">set</span> registry https://registry.npmmirror.com \<br>&amp;&amp; npm install -g pnpm \<br>&amp;&amp; pnpm add -g pm2 ts-node typescript tslib \<br>&amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> -p <span class="hljs-variable">$QL_DIR</span> \<br>&amp;&amp; git <span class="hljs-built_in">clone</span> -b <span class="hljs-variable">$QL_BRANCH</span> https://github.com/whyour/qinglong.git <span class="hljs-variable">$QL_DIR</span> \<br>&amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$QL_DIR</span> \<br>&amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">cp</span> -f .env.example .<span class="hljs-built_in">env</span> \<br>&amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> 777 <span class="hljs-variable">$QL_DIR</span>/shell/*.sh \<br>&amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> 777 <span class="hljs-variable">$QL_DIR</span>/docker/*.sh \<br>&amp;&amp; pnpm install --prod \<br>&amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> -p <span class="hljs-variable">$QL_DIR</span>/static \<br>&amp;&amp; git <span class="hljs-built_in">clone</span> -b <span class="hljs-variable">$QL_BRANCH</span> https://github.com/whyour/qinglong-static.git <span class="hljs-variable">$QL_DIR</span>/static \<br>&amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">ln</span> -s /ql/docker/docker-entrypoint.sh /usr/bin/qinglong \<br>&amp;&amp; qinglong<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure> <div class="group-image-container"><div class="group-image-row"><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/09/15/S30915-07271442_com.termux.jpg"></div><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/09/15/S30915-07332538_com.termux.jpg"></div></div></div><p>7.浏览器输入 127.0.0.1:5700 来访问青龙面板</p><div class="group-image-container"><div class="group-image-row"><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/09/15/S30915-07370295_mark.via.jpg"></div></div></div><h2 id="退出Zerotermux后如何再次打开青龙面板"><a href="#退出Zerotermux后如何再次打开青龙面板" class="headerlink" title="退出Zerotermux后如何再次打开青龙面板"></a>退出Zerotermux后如何再次打开青龙面板</h2><p>1.打开zerotermux后输入startalpine进入容器后再输入qinglong就可以运行青龙面板了</p><div class="group-image-container"><div class="group-image-row"><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/09/15/S30915-07212856_com.termux.jpg"></div><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="https://cdnjson.com/images/2023/09/15/S30915-07413230_com.termux.jpg"></div></div></div>]]></content>
    
    
    
